{"tid":515383,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"小林優結婚了","createTime":"2017-12-31T11:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T08:59:19.000Z","uid":38540,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3ba0226531430fa21a23d86797b6c9e52882c464","tid":515383,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"　　過去曾擔任多位角色配音，繪畫有著獨特個性的日本女性聲優小林優（小林ゆう），於個人推特上公開了結婚消息。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/193008_0e46639dbc6d071cb8d4347ac5ee05f1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F193008_0e46639dbc6d071cb8d4347ac5ee05f1.jpeg&h=a41e5c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n　　小林優為日本知名女性聲優，過去曾擔任《進擊的巨人》莎夏、《命運石之門》漆原琉華、《瑪莉亞狂熱》祇堂鞠也等&hellip;多位角色配音。除了在配音領域上有著亮眼的表現外，其繪畫風格具有十足特色，因此也有著「畫伯」的暱稱。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n十分具有「獨特性」的繪畫風格，也是小林優的特色之一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/193040_cebc5b526fd97996d68db4ddd19af1d3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F193040_cebc5b526fd97996d68db4ddd19af1d3.jpeg&h=21efada5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　就在稍早，小林優於個人的推特上，公開了自己的結婚消息，結婚對象為一般男性。同時小林優表示，之後依舊會以聲優的身份持續努力加油，除了感謝粉絲們一直以來的支持外，也希望未來大家能夠繼續支持著她。"},{"pid":"c1b455f784c3b987ef6a6dbe59915794e907abcf","tid":515383,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T11:46:20.000Z","msg":"畫伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95385e2572a75a7d1310ef387fa96b4dd791006f","tid":515383,"uid":36443,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"係咪母豬新年又ff咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/210953_7df343ae8e32b3fdc115653f5bdc6fac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F210953_7df343ae8e32b3fdc115653f5bdc6fac.jpg&h=7d759b3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"043d43cef77ecfd3c35978cf6494382fc7e74899","tid":515383,"uid":148399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T01:08:27.000Z","msg":"和小林在一起的一般人一定不可能一般"},{"pid":"fd4a8a30ab03411b90b3e76e70ccf5a4b5ee34f3","tid":515383,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T08:59:19.000Z","msg":"遲咗都要講句恭喜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}